description:
Team Foundation Sidekicks is a suite of tools for Microsoft Team Foundation Server administrators and advanced users providing Graphic User Interface for administrative and advanced version control tasks in multi-user TFS environment.
Version 6.0 of Team Foundation Sidekicks is available for Visual Studio© 2015, Team Foundation Server 2015 and Team Foundation Service. .
summary: Team Foundation Sidekicks is a suite of tools for Microsoft Team Foundation Server administrators and advanced users providing Graphic User Interface for administrative and advanced version control tasks in multi-user TFS environments.
